		"Learned React and Node js",
		"Worked on React Frontend to create seamless user experience under the guidance of seniors"
	],
	projects: [
		{
			title: "DataViz",
			description: "At Ekbana, I worked on this DataViz application frontend to develop a data visualization and analytics application. I translated the Figma UI designs to Vue-3.We used Vuex for store management, vue-router and internationalization as well.",
			tools: ["JavaScript", "Vue3 JS", "Vuex", "Docker"]
